content.label:
This game is the best it's really cool and fun
😊😊😊
It is really entertaining. It reminds me of my old game Pokémon snap. So Five stars from me! :D
Keeps my son distracted for hours and it's fun for me too!
It's so good it's better than Pokémon go and tap
Fun!
I like this game. A little confusing as to how to get a good pic. I will learn though. Highly recommend

This is one of the most enjoyable games I've played! From the adorable characters to the mastering of snapshots, it's a great mix of gameplay and discovery. Only regret is the limited film rolls. I want to take so many more pics!
Great game lovely Dino's bootimus quality I love it
Love paying once and having unlimited play. Lots of different dinosaurs and locations and photos to take keep this entertaining.
Awesome game with great graphics. Can play on airplane mode which is dope
Awesome dino game :) love it
Awesome fun
cute fun and addictive

Very relaxing and enjoyable game. But it could really use more lands, as doing the same runs over and over gets really boring, especially if you've played snapimals, which has multiple islands/environments. I'd pay more for a wider selection of Dinos and islands, if only they'd add them!!! Besides that this game is excellent fun.
It's a great way to pass time, and takes an interesting step in the dinosaur category!
I love this game because it is soooooo cute and then the noises make it even cuter
This game is awesome, I love just to go out to the living room and play with my family.😀
This game is well worth the money! The dinosaurs are adorably cute and the gameplay is very fluid and easy to control for it being a mobile game. Very creative and fun!
I don't like the screen tapping to take the picture but it's a well done game
I sorta wish it was easier to get the levels unlocked but overall this game is great. The Dino's are so cute.

Like Pokémon Snap. I've been waiting for a game like this to come around again and here it is finally! Don't always get why some photos are rated higher or lower even when the Dinos are bigger etc. And wish I had more than 5 shots each run. But fun.
It's the Nintendo 64s Pokémon Snap, but with Dino's. Also, you just buy it and play and don't get hammered with ads and inconveniences to make you pay more.
Very relaxing and fun.

I like this version much more than the waiting game that the original requires. I always enjoyed playing the original as a way to relax with fun, colorful, comedic animals, but hated having to wait to earn more camera rolls. I like games where you pay up front and play all you want versus the original pay to play mentality.

The free version is Snapimals but you have to wait for camera rolls and to build things and that's exhausting. 

Other than that, only difference is that there's no wait time and camera rolls are unlimited. And THERES DINOS!
Stats
I got this game because I love dinasours it's so fun it's a lot of adventure
Very cute game, my two daughters LOVE it, but it's very hard for them to get action shots as the Dino's are moving too fast. Well worth it.
I think this game is a fun way to spend your time, but it is expensive.
Basically snap with dinosaurs.  Fun.
Es muy buena la música y los dinos muy tiernos
It's a cool game. Definetly worth the money. Though it closes too fast and should give you more than 5 pics.
I'm training myself to teach my grandson to enjoy the game.
Best game ever
You need to rate the ap in order to complete it. And you need to go on social media with friends in order to unlock all the pictures - two things I don't want my children to have to do!
Great game. Easy to play and kids love it
Such a pleasant game, in my opinion Snapimals was ruined by the in game purchase mechanics, this puts the focus where it should be, an fun and enjoyable game play!
The levels are a little short but there's a lot of variety and it's really fun.
Awesome game!
I love this game, it's very joyful, and it is cute, and I love the graphics.
I wasn't sure at first whether or not this game was worth my time or money, but it's so cute and addicting it's incredible !
Great game to let my daughter to learn dinosaurs! I love it!
Nuff said.
My 3 year old loves this.
It's really fun and worth your money
Relaxing way to waste time. I love that you can buy the game in its entirety. I hope they keep adding content! It is fun to play!
This game is way better than I expected! Lots of fun.

This game is fun to play and feels very polished visually.  I find some of the game mechanics to be strange.  Upgrades are auto-magically managed, but still require user input.  And keys are basically a failed concept which try to trick users into enabling social media.
Love it

This is one of those rare apps that has the ability to transform anyone into a child no matter what your actual age is . I find myself anxiously waiting for the next area to open up so that I can go there myself !
